  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he, being of pure Aryan descent, had no problem, went to the party and they put him in as an-- an Aryan manager-- [SPEAKING GERMAN], the term was-- an Aryan manager.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Hitler came middle of March and the beginning of April, so a couple weeks, three weeks later, a very important looking uniformed guy came in and said they wanted to take my father for a for a deposition.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I was working in the office, not in-- not physically in my father's office, but my father's firm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father came to the office where I was working and said, I have to make a deposition.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this man who took him for the deposition said, and don't you worry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He'll be home for dinner, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, well he came home about a year later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was taken into protective custody, and in a strange way, this too was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] call me stupid.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always look for the silver lining.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was a lifesaver, because he was taken to protective custody, and since they were running out of schools and police stations and other places where they put these [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people that they just grabbed off the street or wherever, they put him into the regular jail with some very interesting burglars and robbers and criminals-- not violent criminals.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And since he never smoked, and they cigarette rations, he could exchange the cigarette ration for a little more food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And since he was such a fine gentlemen, they all were very impressed with the nice gentleman they had among them now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were surprised that he ate beans.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
